title: More national players in New England attended the White House ceremony in 2015 from 2017?
subtitle: Compared with the number of national New England players in the White House event in 2015 and 2017 are real, but misleading.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A series of photographs accurately depicting the number of national players in New England attending the White House ceremony in 2015 and 2017.
